docs.lead_paragraph: Franklin Township asked the New Jersey Department of Transportation to deem a bridge repair project essential, citing the bridge's proximity to a local hospital. The state has halted all non-essential transportation repairs because its transportation trust fund is nearly out of money, causing the bridge to be closed indefinitely.
